    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1937-09-06T05:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1937-09-06T05:00:00-05:00" n="332"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d332">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/9918: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-09-06T19:00:00+09:00"
                            >September 6, 1937—7 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received September 6—6:44 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>351. Our 350, September 6, 1 p.m. Note presented this afternoon to the Foreign
                        Office.<note n="5" xml:id="d332fn5">For text, see <ref
                            target="frus1931-41v01#pg_495">
                            <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, Japan, 1931–1941, vol. <hi
                                rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, p. 495</ref>.</note> The French Ambassador
                    is doing likewise and the British Embassy is still awaiting instructions.<note
                        n="6" xml:id="d332fn6">The British note was presented September 7.</note>
                </p>
                <p>Repeated to Shanghai for information of the Commander-in-Chief and for relay to
                    Nanking.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
